\c 8
\s Ukugcotshwa kukaAroni lamadodana akhe
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Thatha uAroni lamadodana akhe kanye laye\x + Eks. 29.1.\x*, lezembatho\x + Eks. 28.2,4.\x*, lamafutha okugcoba\x + Eks. 30.23-25,30.\x*, lejongosi lomnikelo wesono\x + Eks. 29.1,2.\x*, lenqama ezimbili, lesitsha sezinkwa ezingelamvubelo,
\v 3 ubuthanise inhlangano yonke emnyango wethente lenhlangano.
\v 4 UMozisi wasesenza njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuye, lenhlangano yabuthana emnyango wethente lenhlangano.
\v 5 UMozisi wasesithi enhlanganweni: Yiyo le into iN\nd kosi\nd* elaye ukuthi yenziwe\x + Eks. 29.4.\x*.
\p
\v 6 UMozisi wasesondeza uAroni lamadodana akhe, wabagezisa ngamanzi\x + Eks. 29.4.\x*.
\v 7 Wasemgqokisa isigqoko\x + Eks. 29.5.\x*, wambopha ngebhanti, wamgqokisa ibhatshi, wamfaka \w i-efodi\w**, wambopha ngebhanti le-efodi elelukwe ngobungcitshi, wa\add li\add*bophela kuye ngalo\x + Eks. 29.5.\x*.
\v 8 Wamgqokisa isembatho sesifuba\x + Eks. 28.4.\x*, wabeka esembathweni sesifuba iUrimi leThumimi\x + Eks. 28.30.\x*.
\v 9 Wamthwalisa iqhiye ekhanda lakhe\x + Eks. 28.4; 29.6.\x*; wabeka phezu kweqhiye\x + Eks. 28.36,37; Levi 21.12.\x*, ngaphambi kobuso bayo, incence yegolide, umqhele wobungcwele, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimlayile uMozisi.
\v 10 UMozisi wasethatha amafutha okugcoba\x + Eks. 30.26-29.\x*, waligcoba ithabhanekele lakho konke okuphakathi kwalo, wakungcwelisa.
\v 11 Wafafaza ngawo phezu kwelathi kasikhombisa, wagcoba ilathi lezitsha zalo zonke, lenditshi yokugezela lonyawo lwayo, ukukungcwelisa.
\v 12 Wathela okwamafutha okugcoba ekhanda likaAroni\x + Eks. 29.7; 30.30. Levi 21.10,12. Hlab. 133.2.\x*, wamgcoba, ukumngcwelisa.
\v 13 UMozisi wasesondeza amadodana kaAroni\x + Eks. 29.8,9.\x*, wawagqokisa izigqoko, wawabopha ngamabhanti, wawathwalisa izingowane, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimlayile uMozisi.
\p
\v 14 Wasesondeza ijongosi lomnikelo wesono\x + Eks. 29.10. Hez. 43.19.\x*; uAroni lamadodana akhe basebebeka izandla zabo enhlokweni yejongosi lomnikelo wesono\x + 4.4.\x*.
\v 15 Waselihlaba, uMozisi wasethatha igazi\x + Eks. 29.12,36. Levi 4.7. Hez. 43.20,26. Heb. 9.22.\x*, walifaka ngomunwe wakhe empondweni zelathi inhlangothi zonke, wahlambulula ilathi, wathululela igazi kungaphansi yelathi, walingcwelisa ukulenzela inhlawulo yokuthula.
\v 16 Wathatha idanga lonke\x + 3.4.\x*, lamahwahwa esibindi, lezinso zombili lamahwahwa azo, uMozisi wakutshisa elathini.
\v 17 Kodwa ijongosi, lesikhumba salo, lenyama yalo, lomswane walo wakutshisa ngomlilo ngaphandle kwenkamba, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimlayile uMozisi\x + Eks. 29.14-18. Levi 4.11,12.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Wasesondeza inqama yomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Eks. 29.15. Levi 8.2.\x*; uAroni lamadodana akhe basebebeka izandla zabo phezu kwenhloko yenqama.
\v 19 Waseyihlaba, uMozisi wafafaza igazi phezu kwelathi inhlangothi zonke\x + 1.8.\x*.
\v 20 Waseyisika inqama ngeziqa zayo, uMozisi watshisa inhloko lezitho lamahwahwa.
\v 21 Wagezisa imibilini lemilenze ngamanzi, uMozisi watshisa inqama yonke elathini, kungumnikelo wokutshiswa oloqhatshi olumnandi, kungumnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, njengalokho iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimlayile uMozisi.
\p
\v 22 Wasesondeza enye inqama\x + Eks. 29.19,31. Levi 8.2.\x*, inqama yokwehlukaniswa; uAroni lamadodana akhe basebebeka izandla zabo phezu kwenhloko yenqama.
\v 23 Waseyihlaba, uMozisi wathatha okwegazi layo, walifaka eqwangeni lwendlebe yokunene kaAroni, lesithupheni sesandla sakhe sokunene, lezwaneni olukhulu lonyawo lwakhe lokunene.
\v 24 Wasesondeza amadodana kaAroni, uMozisi wafaka okwegazi eqwangeni lwendlebe yawo yokunene, lesithupheni sesandla sawo sokunene, lezwaneni olukhulu lonyawo lwawo lokunene; uMozisi wasefafaza igazi phezu kwelathi inhlangothi zonke.
\v 25 Wasethatha amahwahwa\x + Eks. 29.22.\x*, lomsila ononileyo, ledanga lonke, lamahwahwa esibindi, lezinso zombili lamahwahwa azo, lomlenze wokunene,
\v 26 wakhupha esitsheni sezinkwa ezingelamvubelo\x + Eks. 29.23; Levi 8.2.\x* esasiphambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* iqebelengwana laba linye elingelamvubelo, leqebelengwana elilodwa lesinkwa esilamafutha, lesinkwana esisodwa esiyisipatalala, wakubeka phezu kwamahwahwa laphezu komlenze wokunene;
\v 27 wakubeka konke ezandleni zikaAroni lezandleni zamadodana akhe\x + Eks. 29.24.\x*, wakuzunguza kwaba ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 28 UMozisi wasekuthatha ezandleni zabo, wakutshisa elathini phezu komnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Eks. 29.25.\x*, kwaba yikwehlukaniswa okoqhatshi olumnandi, kungumnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 29 UMozisi wasethatha isifuba, wasizunguza saba ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; saba yisabelo sikaMozisi senqama yokwehlukaniswa\x + Eks. 29.26.\x*, njengalokho iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimlayile uMozisi.
\v 30 UMozisi wasethatha okwamafutha okugcoba\x + Eks. 29.21; 30.30; Nani 3.3.\x* lokwegazi okwakuphezu kwelathi, wakufafaza phezu kukaAroni, phezu kwezembatho zakhe, laphezu kwamadodana akhe, laphezu kwezembatho zamadodana akhe kanye laye. Wamngcwelisa uAroni, izembatho zakhe, lamadodana akhe, lezembatho zamadodana akhe kanye laye.
\p
\v 31 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni lemadodaneni akhe: Phekani inyama\x + Eks. 29.31,32.\x* emnyango wethente lenhlangano, liyidle lapho lezinkwa ezisesitsheni sokwehlukaniswa, njengokulaya kwami ngisithi: UAroni lamadodana akhe bazakudla.
\v 32 Lokuseleyo kwenyama lokwezinkwa lizakutshisa ngomlilo\x + Eks. 29.34.\x*.
\v 33 Njalo kaliyikuphuma ngomnyango wethente lenhlangano, insuku eziyisikhombisa, kuze kufike usuku okuzagcwaliswa ngalo insuku zokwehlukaniswa kwenu, ngoba uzalehlukanisa okwensuku eziyisikhombisa\x + Eks. 29.30,35. Hez. 43.25,26.\x*.
\v 34 Njengoba enzile lamuhla iN\nd kosi\nd* ilayile ukukwenza, ukulenzela inhlawulo yokuthula.
\v 35 Ngakho lizahlala emnyango wethente\x + Nani 3.7.9.19. Dute. 11.1; 1 Kho. 2.3. Zek. 3.7.\x* lenhlangano insuku eziyisikhombisa, imini lebusuku, ligcine imfanelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* ukuze lingafi; ngoba ngilaywe njalo.
\v 36 UAroni lamadodana akhe basebesenza izinto zonke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazilayayo ngesandla sikaMozisi.